ChangeLog for package mySA

changes in version 0.2 (2018-08-29)
Restructured:
  - Function has been restructured: code was simplified and computational
    burden decreased by vectorised programming; output was restructured and input
    arguments adapted accordingly. Old version as been kept as vbsa_old()

changes in version 0.1.3 (2018-08-29)
  - monitor_indices:
  - Full sensitivity index matrices (N-by-K) can be returned if desired
    instead of just the final indices after N resamplings.
changed:
  - initial release
fixed:
  - missing ChangeLog

changes in version 0.1.2 (2018-08-28)
parallel:
  - Added argument 'ncores' to allow for parallel evaluation of fn (employs
    package doMC; Linux only!)

changes in version 0.1.1 (2018-08-28)
  - param_names:
  - Parameter names will be given to fn, i.e. the first argument of fn now
    recieves a named vector of parameter realisation

